title: Pikachu's thunderbolt malfunctioning
description: Pikachu's thunderbolt attack has been misfiring and causing some serious damage to our gym battles. Please fix asap!

title: Charizard's tail on fire!
description: Our beloved Charizard's tail has caught on fire! Quick, someone get a Squirtle to put it out!

title: Snorlax blocking office doorway
description: Snorlax has decided to take a nap in the middle of the office doorway, causing a major traffic jam. Can someone please wake him up?

title: Jigglypuff singing loudly
description: There's a Jigglypuff singing at the top of its lungs and it's driving everyone in the office crazy. Please send a team to catch it and return it to its trainer before it gives us all permanent hearing damage.

title: Squirtle flooding the bathroom
description: There's a Squirtle in the bathroom and it's causing a flood. Water is spilling out into the hallway and it's a mess. Please send a team to catch it and return it to its trainer before it causes any more damage.

title: Jigglypuff serenading the office!
description: Jigglypuff has taken up residence in the office and won't stop singing. Please send a team to remove it before our ears bleed.

title: Psyduck causing brain freeze
description: We've discovered that a Psyduck's presence is causing a sudden outbreak of brain freeze in the office. Please send a team to investigate and put an end to this icy misery.

title: Snorlax blocking the hallway
description: A Snorlax has taken up residence in the middle of the hallway and refuses to move. Please send a team to relocate it before it causes a traffic jam.

title: Squirtle flooding the bathroom
description: A Squirtle has somehow managed to turn on all the faucets in the bathroom, causing a flood. Please send a team to capture it and stop the waterworks.

title: Goldeen causing a commotion
description: A Goldeen has been causing a ruckus in the office, flopping around and knocking things over. Please send a team to tranquilize it and restore peace.

title: Drowzee putting the office to sleep
description: A Drowzee has been spotted wandering the office, and people are starting to nod off wherever they stand. Please send a team to capture it before productivity grinds to a halt.

title: Pidgey infestation in the server room
description: We've discovered a Pidgey nest in the server room and they're causing all sorts of problems. Please send a team to remove them before they cause a data breach.

title: Caterpie eating all the office plants
description: A Caterpie has been feasting on all the office plants and we're running out of greenery. Please send a team to capture it and save our foliage.

title: Koffing filling the office with gas
description: A Koffing has been releasing gas all over the office, and it's getting hard to breathe. Please send a team to capture it and ventilate the area.

title: Abra teleporting objects around the office
description: An Abra has been teleporting objects around the office, causing chaos. Please send a team to capture it and put an end to the magic tricks.

title: Gengar's shadow ball causing server lag
description: Gengar's shadow ball attack is causing some serious lag on our servers. Can someone please fix this ghostly issue?

title: Jynx's seductive singing causing distraction
description: Jynx has been singing her seductive melodies in the office and it's causing major distraction among the employees. Can someone please make her stop?
